history.content:
Venture Strategy Solutions at UC Berkeley is working with Canva on a research project this semester. We are looking to learn how you create and complete assignments for your studies at UC Berkeley. How you create designs for both in studies or any personal / side projects.  What tools do you use and how do you use them? 

We have created a short survey, which takes around 10 minutes to complete, and would love to hear from you. These responses will help Canva shape their future product vision on their university offering. We would like to remind you that all details you shared will remain confidential. 

As a thank you for your completion, each respondent will receive a $25 Canva print coupon which you can use to print a fun tote bag/T-shirt/etc on Canva. 

 https://berkeley.qualtrics.com/jfe/form/SV_2i9W3ahmJPWCzpI
history.subject: Please take a few minutes to fill this survey (Get giftcard worth $25!)
